            <title>[SOLR-15826] ResourceLoader should better respect allowed paths</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15826</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ResourceLoader only returns files relative to instanceDir or resources from Classpath, but we have a few file-exists checks that are done prior to these checks, which can cause weird bugs. In this issue we&apos;ll clean up this, along with a few refactorings and code simplifications.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
